What is git?
    Version Control
    Snapshot
    To add data
    Integrity

Three States
    modified, staged, committed  (local git database)


Installing Git:


Install home-brew
********************
/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)"

To Install git
********************
brew install git

Commands
*********

git --version       //gives git version
git status             // status of changes
git add             //to stage the files
git diff               //not just what you changed but which files you changed



